description: [Account Types][Default to Savings] transfer from default (Checking) account to savings account
[Account Types][Default to Checking] transfer from default (Checking) account to checking account
[Account Types][Saving to Checking] transfer from savings to checking account
[Account Types][Checking to Saving] transfer from checking to savings account
[Account Types][Saving to Default] transfer from savings to default (Checking) account
[Account Types][Checking to Default] transfer from checking to default (Checking) account
[Account Types][Saving to Saving] transfer from savings to another savings account
[Account Types][Checking to Checking] transfer from Checking to another Checking account
[Rounding][Round Up] transfer should round amounts to the nearest second decimal digit (round up)
[Rounding][Round Down] transfer should round amounts to the nearest second decimal digit (round down)
